text: Horrible! I called in a family order of bread sticks with cheese plus 2 extra sauces. Got there 25 minutes later to pick it up, as instructed. They hadn't even put it in the oven yet. I didn't say a word, things happen, I patiently waited. …More

text: To every one who is complaining about this pizza hut I as a pizza hut employee deeply apologize for all the mistakes, misplaced deals, and anything else that was awful. I hope that in the future the store gets better and gets your business back.
